TITLE: Episode 133 - Formed From Dust with Sara the Dirt Lady
DESCRIPTION: This week, we are joined by Sara the Irish Dirty Lady. She is a soil scientist, a Christian, and from the emerald isle. We will dig into the relationship between humanity and the earth, rest, worship, and more. Join us as we drill into the ground beneath us.
